<h1>Why the ChetSite?</h1>
    <div class="whatisbody">
<p>While working on this project a lot of problems arose that needed a specific skill set, one that was heavily geared towards the mindset of a designer. How problems were handled, how time was managed, and even more specified things such as prop production, storyboarding and color theory were improved from a designer’s perspective. This project provides documentation on the pre-production, production and post production. 
This website is not only built to show off that perspective, but also to highlight all the other aspects that made this project such an important memory for all involved. This site’s primary purpose is documentation and appreciation for the project and all involved.
</p>
    </div>


